prototype:

The Student Project Task Management System is a web-based application designed to help student development teams efficiently manage their academic projects. It provides a centralized platform where users can create projects, assign tasks, set deadlines, track progress, and monitor team activities.

Key Features:

* User Authentication (Login/Register)
* Project Creation and Management
* Task Assignment
* Deadline Tracking
* Progress Monitoring Dashboard
* Status Updates (Pending, In Progress, Completed)
* Notifications and Reminders

Technologies Used:

* HTML
* CSS
* JavaScript
* MySQL Database

Objective:

To improve team collaboration, increase productivity, and ensure timely completion of student projects through effective task management and progress tracking. 🚀
